<p>Travel by Eurostar on a Saturday with <strong>free</strong> ski carriage and transfer direct to resort. Friday departures are on request.</p>
<ul>
<li>3 alighting points – London St. Pancras, Ebbsfleet or Ashford International - all direct to your French station</li>
<li>Larger luggage allowance - 2 suitcases plus your skis or snowboard</li>
<li>Food included in Standard Premier</li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> Wi-Fi onboard</li>
<li>Check-in up to one-hour before departure</li>
<li>Spacious seating and travel</li>
<li>Short transfers to resort</li>
</ul>
<p><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/getting-to-resort/rail#winter" target="_blank" title="Getting to Resort by Rail">See full details here &gt;&gt;&gt;</a></p>
<p> </p>
